description: 2005 Blazer Bay 2170 with a 2008 Suzuki DF 175.  Just under 500 hours on Motor, a few less for the hull.  The boat was purchased used in 2007 with 36 hours on it and mine since then. The boat has two livewells, 80lb i-pilot (never used), Raymarine Dragonfly 7, Bluetooth stereo with four speakers. If you are familiar with the Blazer bay 2170 you will note that it is the best of the "Rolled-gunnel" boats.  It is fully composite so no rot, light, efficient and does very well in chop.
